    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i rly do feel alone tho. even when im around people i feel like there's this huge wall between me and them. like i'm just watching a movie of life instead of living it. it feels like no matter how hard i try to bridge that gap, i'm just gonna be an outsider forever. it's just... a lot to carry every single day.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
